{"tid":1637574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要死線 射返個波卑港共","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:36:03.000Z","uid":245041,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"81afa2d4d788a5470d7b9bfea7d60fb34b3e6dfd","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"和勇和勇<br />\n一路4個月都係咁走<br />\n我地條死線去左邊？<br />\n依家政府係希望label我地係恐怖主義 我地要拎返主導權<br />\nset死線叫政府回應 射波卑佢 <br />\n卑5日 淨係做和理活動 再透過民間記者會宣布死線<br />\n否則不合作活動會升級 <br />\n<br />\n唔係要停 係要用智慧係取消 勇武停幾日 <br />\n3日都得 就係要射個波卑政 還掂呢幾日要返工 就set返死線好冇？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n驅逐共產 還我香我！"},{"pid":"6aa4bbe8435676a6142557b40deb075fc1c684bd","tid":1637574,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"死線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果大家覺得資訊混亂 幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">開設行動台</span><br />\n［連仔入］全部人幫手推 資訊進化論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637449</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5de742d93e38a318135d3187b8ea2eded502cd00","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:43:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0188944b9499471ad1ecccd98bc13e3911e13790","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d982d2464b9083a4a50034254a5abe0c2d56288c","tid":1637574,"uid":218907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9132133a386843fc5f0ae5b67562a47b7e60b5a9","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ec5e28a2a8ed8fd63db5c87f122aa61a5f5f9a3","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"我地條死線係邊啊<br />\n全部人入來"},{"pid":"baf76471b62fa64505c5c9738c570163b490926a","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"我要死線我要死線<br />\n我要死線我要死線"},{"pid":"0ff5d532a0c76468d251c4cedd9fbdd4b53ed893","tid":1637574,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:05:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e824ff9eb65642b0382772a0cd1bab5c87631c61","tid":1637574,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:07:30.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"e7963081d08fbc7517c2beb11fd76a061bd9f76b","tid":1637574,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"同意！"},{"pid":"a69d884c723f5f7e0203afa31699b844d4e46169","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97d46e343a1366d2e8b68f3cb9a312a468001352","tid":1637574,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n港共春袋係金融體系<br />\n繼續㩒atm make noise 各大傳媒淡化處理呢d事 其實幫緊港共維穩<br />\n銀行call loan 引發支爆 中共到時就會投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ac5378dc267ce1bd621dfed6a185f86114f579c7","tid":1637574,"uid":71656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"死線過左要點升級<br />\n想點升級"},{"pid":"937886ae760a7b36fb164e85843d7e04597ef84c","tid":1637574,"uid":71656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"最理想一定係有狗就燒<br />\n打到班狗驚<br />\n無左狗 <br />\n佢即刻跪"},{"pid":"5e2b696565c7e0375c8b4725a4befb8376bd9468","tid":1637574,"uid":186874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n（幫推上熱門）可唔可以推返啲正經野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"65ff4289864ef4c123dfbeb0c1aaac7b6ae98f37","tid":1637574,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67644eaa8f94248375710994db7443110c240d28","tid":1637574,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"推啦 <br />\n有勇有謀 香港人！"},{"pid":"8f2f0fbd41ccc5897a48d34f1ae6787c0db978ab","tid":1637574,"uid":206819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<br />\n我地要設個死線 仲要係對外宣布 唔係的自己圍爐定時間<br />\n要張個限期係有影響力<br />\n公佈左時間之後 要迫個政府正面回應民市既訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫停勇武 暫停裝修 暫停私了</span></span> <br />\n因為個政府一定都以「反暴力」「止暴制亂」去做藉口<br />\n所以當香港平息既時候 政府都冇其他理由唔正面回應民意<br />\n一來依段時間可以養兵儲裝備 二來減低民怨 三來降低示威者「暴力」既形象<br />\n唔代表依段時間冇野做 可以繼<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣 民間記者會</span></span> 話比全港/全世界知依段時間發生咩事 最好打下感情牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要公開發聲明 會停止一切活動 個deadline唔可以太短<br />\n短則一星期 長則二/三星期<br />\n因為要比時間等依件事擴大引起關注 比足時間政府都唔回應/否決我地既訴求既話 道理就係我地到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果政府係限期之內 唔應承 就武力升級！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開初唔洗講比政府知 咁樣好似用暴力威迫政府<br />\n我地咁和善既香港人係唔會做咁缺德既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就近deadline既時候 可以屌鳩政府唔回應唔聽民意<br />\n所以我地先會武力升級 交返個波比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a253fe902e00618cc9815efda11ccd32d680227","tid":1637574,"uid":206819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:34:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af584e372c8c168ceb822f879c29e90f61d71b88","tid":1637574,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2f0fbd41ccc5897a48d34f1ae6787c0db978ab","tid":1637574,"uid":206819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推<br />\n我地要設個死線 仲要係對外宣布 唔係的自己圍爐定時間<br />\n要張個限期係有影響力<br />\n公佈左時間之後 要迫個政府正面回應民市既訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫停勇武 暫停裝修 暫停私了</span></span> <br />\n因為個政府一定都以「反暴力」「止暴制亂」去做藉口<br />\n所以當香港平息既時候 政府都冇其他理由唔正面回應民意<br />\n一來依段時間可以養兵儲裝備 二來減低民怨 三來降低示威者「暴力」既形象<br />\n唔代表依段時間冇野做 可以繼<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣 民間記者會</span></span> 話比全港/全世界知依段時間發生咩事 最好打下感情牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要公開發聲明 會停止一切活動 個deadline唔可以太短<br />\n短則一星期 長則二/三星期<br />\n因為要比時間等依件事擴大引起關注 比足時間政府都唔回應/否決我地既訴求既話 道理就係我地到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果政府係限期之內 唔應承 就武力升級！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開初唔洗講比政府知 咁樣好似用暴力威迫政府<br />\n我地咁和善既香港人係唔會做咁缺德既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就近deadline既時候 可以屌鳩政府唔回應唔聽民意<br />\n所以我地先會武力升級 交返個波比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"有病咩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"